high_descs: Walk forward just past the coffee table, then turn left and walk to the red sofa.
Pick up the credit card from the sofa.
Turn left and walk forward to the tall lamp in the corner by the red armchair.
anns.task_desc: Examine a credit card by the light of a floor lamp.

high_descs: Go across to the edge of the carpet then turn left and go to the edge of the carpet then turn left then right to face the end of the sofa
Pick up the credit card from the sofa
Turn left and go to the wall then turn right and raise the credit card up to the lamp shade
anns.task_desc: Examine a credit card under the light of a floor lamp

high_descs: Go left and face the left side of the couch.
Pick the credit card up from the couch.
Turn to the left and cross the room and then turn to the right to face the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Pick up a credit card and turn a lamp on.
